node.text: our hard lemonade has just been named the official sponsor of the long weekend. also the official sponsor of bbqs. also of the beach. also of your friends boat. in stores now. not cider, not seltzer, lemonade.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by downeast cider house in Downeast Cider House. May be an image of drink, outdoors and text that says 'EDOWNEAST THE UNFILTERED UNFI CRAFT CIDER'.

node.text: deep summer-our highly limited, taproom only, 10% abv mango guava cider-is coming back. we’ve only made a few hundred cases and once it’s gone, it’s gone. available monday at noon for pre-sale. also is noon am or pm

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by downeast cider house in Downeast Cider House with @shotbysurette. May be an image of drink.

node.text: after a huge run in the taproom this summer-we’ve canned a super limited amount of our hard lemonade. not a cider. not a tea. it’s all [5% abv] lemonade. in stores now-unless you’ve waited too long to read this oh no

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by downeast cider house in Downeast Cider House. May be an image of food and outdoors.

node.text: allow us to introduce the newest taproom exclusive-orange creamsicle. available in the taproom now. cold, refreshing, and inspired by saving up for ice cream, 100 degree days, and a moment of misguided vacation inspiration after one too many ciders (dm for details on that story)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by downeast cider house in Downeast Cider House. May be an image of drink.

node.text: please don’t tell us it’s too early for pumpkin to come back. when’s the correct time? september? september was 11 months ago. if anything, we’re late. so apologies for being late-pumpkin is back in stores now.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by downeast cider house in Maverick's, East Boston with @maverickseastboston. May be an image of 1 person and bottle.

node.text: why does everyone assume summer is over as if august doesn’t exist? it’s still tea time. we’re introducing tea thursdays. from this point forward we will post everyone’s best tea photos, every thursday. do not hold us to any of this. this actually might be the last tea thursday. enjoy it.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by downeast cider house in Downeast Cider House. May be an image of one or more people and outdoors.

node.text:
right on the pier outside the taproom-our outdoor bar is open and ready. every weekend, all summer. full pours, ciders, teas,
food. come on down. tag 38 friends you’re coming with.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by downeast cider house in Downeast Cider House.

node.text:
quick data check shows strawberry season is responsible for a 671 percent uptick in picnics in the early going - big numbers let’s see if we can keep it going

available in: stores, the cider house, our outdoor bar, wicker baskets

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by downeast cider house in Downeast Cider House. May be an image of fruit.

node.text:
the taproom and outdoor bar are closed tomorrow for our first company party in years but we wanted to let you know that —peach bellini—will be waiting for you on friday. sweet peach with a hint of champagne flavor. 

mimosa can’t be the only champagne inspired cider in the world. 

a taproom exclusive

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by downeast cider house on July 13, 2021. May be an image of strawberry and drink.

node.text: from the cider house to a can. a lot of cans actually. a strawberry success story. grab some now. all fresh, sweet strawberry flavor. you’re a loaf of bread, some peanut butter and a fancy blanket away from a picnic.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by downeast cider house in Downeast Cider House. May be an image of drink and outdoors.

node.text: edit-pop up opening saturday. introducing fruit punch. tasting notes? fruit punch. also, it’s exclusive to our-outdoor-full pour-pop up bar which opens [saturday] at 11am-and open thu-sun all summer long. located in the shipyard, right outside the cider house. see you there. see you tomorrow night. full pours. wow. what a time.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by downeast cider house in Downeast Cider House. May be an image of drink and indoor.

node.text:
re-introducing prickly pear. not a pear. not prickly. it’s inspired by a margarita but let’s be honest the real star of the show is the color. (and the 7.5 abv). 

stock up now for the long weekend-we’re closed on sunday.
